And there's no blog post here.

00:23:02.590 --> 00:23:03.700
You created Blogger.

00:23:03.700 --> 00:23:05.084
You sold it to Google, right?

00:23:05.084 --> 00:23:06.250
People wrote their thoughts.

00:23:06.250 --> 00:23:07.450
It was full thoughts.

00:23:07.450 --> 00:23:08.617
And now you're saying just--

00:23:08.617 --> 00:23:10.866
it's the same as blogger
except without the blog post.

00:23:10.866 --> 00:23:11.900
It's just the title.

00:23:11.900 --> 00:23:13.010
HEATH ROWE: And now
it's back to medium.

00:23:13.010 --> 00:23:13.930
JASON CALACANIS:
Right, and I was

00:23:13.930 --> 00:23:16.013
like, you realize that if
this succeeds it's going

00:23:16.013 --> 00:23:17.560
to be a cacophony of idiots?

00:23:17.560 --> 00:23:21.430
Like literally everybody
who can't put together

00:23:21.430 --> 00:23:24.580
a blog post, which
is only 400 words,

00:23:24.580 --> 00:23:26.650
they're going to write
140 characters instead

00:23:26.650 --> 00:23:28.936
of 140 or 300 words.

00:23:28.936 --> 00:23:30.310
Every idiot in
the world is going

00:23:30.310 --> 00:23:32.290
to be on this thing all
day saying stupid things,

00:23:32.290 --> 00:23:34.373
and it's going to be getting
magnified like crazy.

00:23:34.373 --> 00:23:36.700
I was absolutely right.

00:23:36.700 --> 00:23:38.194
And it cost me $50 million.

00:23:38.194 --> 00:23:39.610
So then I realized,
you know what?

00:23:39.610 --> 00:23:41.020
I don't have to know.

00:23:41.020 --> 00:23:43.480
If there is a Jason's
law of angel investing,

00:23:43.480 --> 00:23:46.060
it's I don't need to know if
your idea is going to succeed.

00:23:46.060 --> 00:23:48.020
I just need to know if
you're going to succeed.

00:23:48.020 --> 00:23:50.870
So since I started that
approach to angel investing,

00:23:50.870 --> 00:23:52.980
which is does this
person have passion?

00:23:52.980 --> 00:23:54.370
Do they have skill?

00:23:54.370 --> 00:23:57.220
Do they understand how to
build a product and a team?

00:23:57.220 --> 00:23:58.600
I look for those traits.

00:23:58.600 --> 00:24:01.510
And when you ask people
questions, short questions--

00:24:01.510 --> 00:24:02.650
what are you working on?

00:24:02.650 --> 00:24:04.084
Why will this idea work now?

00:24:04.084 --> 00:24:05.500
Has something
changed in the world

00:24:05.500 --> 00:24:07.150
that makes this idea work now?

00:24:07.150 --> 00:24:10.150
Or tell me about
the product design.

00:24:10.150 --> 00:24:11.302
Or why are you doing this?

00:24:11.302 --> 00:24:13.760
Just like literally pointing
out one feature of the product

00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:16.270
to say, what does this
syndication thing,

00:24:16.270 --> 00:24:18.850
this little snippet here on
YouTube, why is that important?

00:24:18.850 --> 00:24:21.430
