to ask Chad early

00:24:21.430 --> 00:24:24.044
that, he was like, oh,
because people want

00:24:24.044 --> 00:24:25.210
to put videos on their site.

00:24:25.210 --> 00:24:26.240
There's no easy way to do it.

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:27.448
They have to put up a server.

00:24:27.448 --> 00:24:30.550
So if they put this JavaScript
into their blogger, dotcom

00:24:30.550 --> 00:24:32.627
account, they could put
a video on their site.

00:24:32.627 --> 00:24:33.710
Oh, why is that important?

00:24:33.710 --> 00:24:35.419
Well, because it's
free marketing for us.

00:24:35.419 --> 00:24:37.126
We're giving them free
hosting of videos.

00:24:37.126 --> 00:24:39.050
They give us free marketing
to their audience,

00:24:39.050 --> 00:24:40.925
and we're going to grow
the service that way.

00:24:40.925 --> 00:24:44.430
That was the why now
syndication and cloud computing.

