If you know somebody
is a winner, if you

00:26:01.960 --> 00:26:03.460
know they work, if you
know they're passionate,

00:26:03.460 --> 00:26:05.168
if you know they're
not going to give up,

00:26:05.168 --> 00:26:07.390
these are the qualities
