00:29:07.450 --> 00:29:09.526
And it's like, well, if
you have a great team,

00:29:09.526 --> 00:29:11.150
and a great company,
and great product,

00:29:11.150 --> 00:29:14.320
and customers who love you,
and some level of traction,

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:16.750
you're going to
meet 100 investors.

00:29:16.750 --> 00:29:19.300
