00:32:43.554 --> 00:32:45.345
that makes it a very
attractive investment.

00:32:45.345 --> 00:32:47.760
It's like, this person's
not going to give up.

00:32:47.760 --> 00:32:52.440
And that's a-- at least you
know that your money didn't

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:55.951
get burned without
people even trying.

00:32:55.951 --> 00:32:57.450
It's nice to know
that people tried,

00:32:57.450 --> 00:32:59.158
and I don't mind people
losing the money,

00:32:59.158 --> 00:33:00.940
as long as they tried hard.

00:33:00.940 --> 00:33:04.070
That's really the goal.

